notes
This is a joint experiment with contributions from Norway (Cesar La Hoz),
third-party (Wayne Scales) and the UK (Mike Kosch).

The VHF (pointing vertically), UHF and MORRO radars will be used together with
the HF facility which will also operate partly in radar mode.

